{"tw": {"1526900": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Sapphire Safari", "steam_appid": 1526900, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<h1>藍圖</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/8ac1df5d4a33f66795a15a0ec3238883.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Sapphire Safari</i> 仍處於早期開發階段，許多令人興奮的功能即將推出！請閱讀我們的開發者日誌，了解更多即將上線的內容。以下任務沒有特定順序，我們的目標是全部完成！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/fa2705f7f034d4f6bdce5f1579b62caa.avif?t=1775571253\" width=956 height=608 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/a0be4ce39685138a23db4534a666fd8e.avif?t=1775571253\" width=800 height=146 /></span></p></p><br><h1>SYSTEM SPECS</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Sapphire Safari</i> 在大多數系統上表現良好，包括現代集成顯卡的設備。我們已在 Windows 11 的桌上型電腦和筆記型電腦上進行測試。最重要的硬體配置是高速 SSD 儲存裝置和足夠的 VRAM。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/f178dd50f7afda5a12e182335afe6635.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=384 /></span></p></p><br><h1>關於此遊戲</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/ab0708cdff7a4d5cc7666a82d9d3edd2.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <i>Sapphire Safari</i> 中回應野性的召喚！這是一款開放世界的攝影冒險遊戲！捕捉怪物女孩在自然環境中的美麗身影。作為野生動物攝影師，你的任務是深入未知領域，記錄她們的社交、狩獵、睡眠、交配行為……並希望能夠平安返回。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/b79027c7dee445d8849b0a758efc1ef4.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/1b37f5b34566df86b96177b9eb4433cf.poster.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/1b37f5b34566df86b96177b9eb4433cf.webm?t=1775571253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/1b37f5b34566df86b96177b9eb4433cf.mp4?t=1775571253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sapphire 島神秘地被發現，一支勇敢的科學家團隊被派遣前往揭開它的秘密。一片充滿獨特野生動物的處女地……這是一次令人驚嘆的發現！誰不想抓住這樣的機會？一個月後，科學團隊與基地失去聯繫。接下來會發生什麼？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/08432378b5b967485a5b50247425ac29.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/c6b06392a3d29eaaf33e179de44de5e5.poster.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/c6b06392a3d29eaaf33e179de44de5e5.webm?t=1775571253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/c6b06392a3d29eaaf33e179de44de5e5.mp4?t=1775571253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演一名追求榮耀與名聲的野生動物攝影師！沿著科學團隊的足跡，揭開他們的命運，同時用你的相機記錄整個島嶼的壯麗景色！用異國風情的照片、姿勢、交配場景和親密瞬間填滿怪物百科全書！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/9bbbdf9ec049c0146c009de38ad2455f.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/48cbb11059f92f48df10fe2c117bc015.poster.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/48cbb11059f92f48df10fe2c117bc015.webm?t=1775571253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/48cbb11059f92f48df10fe2c117bc015.mp4?t=1775571253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sapphire 島上生活著各種獨特的野生生物，但不是所有生物都友好。小心翼翼地潛行在地形中，盡量避免被發現——島上的掠食者們可喜歡美味的獵物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/8affe337698e7244f273590964db152c.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/651652f7fd34c922955df0b5168c9b7d.poster.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/651652f7fd34c922955df0b5168c9b7d.webm?t=1775571253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/651652f7fd34c922955df0b5168c9b7d.mp4?t=1775571253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與當地生物建立關係！與她們相處的時間越長，她們就會變得更加友好。主動發起親密互動，參加有趣的活動，讓野生動物為你擺姿勢！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/eff6cd0229f0b43efa3c719729bb1c58.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成百科全書，見證每一個親密行為，找回遺失的探險日誌，探索島嶼，解鎖所有成就，發現隱藏的危險，還有更多！<i>Sapphire Safari</i> 提供了豐富的目標和等待發現的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索充滿怪物女孩的環境</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由業界專業人士全程配音</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索眾多獨特地點，拍攝並記錄野生動物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與怪物女孩在她們獨特的棲息地建立連結，體驗全新感覺</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提供多樣化性偏好，自由自訂體驗！Anthro 愛好者的天堂！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成你的百科全書，發現所有秘密！為收藏愛好者帶來豐富挑戰</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >日夜交替，晴天、暴雨或風暴！Sapphire 島根據動態天氣系統變化</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分享你的快照！每張拍攝的照片都會生成可分享的圖片，非常適合展示你的攝影技巧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>注意：</strong>我們的翻譯由人工智慧引擎提供支持，可能不是 100% 準確。</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/ab0708cdff7a4d5cc7666a82d9d3edd2.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <i>Sapphire Safari</i> 中回應野性的召喚！這是一款開放世界的攝影冒險遊戲！捕捉怪物女孩在自然環境中的美麗身影。作為野生動物攝影師，你的任務是深入未知領域，記錄她們的社交、狩獵、睡眠、交配行為……並希望能夠平安返回。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/b79027c7dee445d8849b0a758efc1ef4.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span 