bdf9ec049c0146c009de38ad2455f.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/48cbb11059f92f48df10fe2c117bc015.poster.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/48cbb11059f92f48df10fe2c117bc015.webm?t=1775571253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/48cbb11059f92f48df10fe2c117bc015.mp4?t=1775571253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sapphire 島上生活著各種獨特的野生生物，但不是所有生物都友好。小心翼翼地潛行在地形中，盡量避免被發現——島上的掠食者們可喜歡美味的獵物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/8affe337698e7244f273590964db152c.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/651652f7fd34c922955df0b5168c9b7d.poster.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/651652f7fd34c922955df0b5168c9b7d.webm?t=1775571253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/651652f7fd34c922955df0b5168c9b7d.mp4?t=1775571253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與當地生物建立關係！與她們相處的時間越長，她們就會變得更加友好。主動發起親密互動，參加有趣的活動，讓野生動物為你擺姿勢！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/eff6cd0229f0b43efa3c719729bb1c58.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成百科全書，見證每一個親密行為，找回遺失的探險日誌，探索島嶼，解鎖所有成就，發現隱藏的危險，還有更多！<i>Sapphire Safari</i> 提供了豐富的目標和等待發現的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索充滿怪物女孩的環境</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由業界專業人士全程配音</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索眾多獨特地點，拍攝並記錄野生動物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與怪物女孩在她們獨特的棲息地建立連結，體驗全新感覺</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提供多樣化性偏好，自由自訂體驗！Anthro 愛好者的天堂！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成你的百科全書，發現所有秘密！為收藏愛好者帶來豐富挑戰</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >日夜交替，晴天、暴雨或風暴！Sapphire 島根據動態天氣系統變化</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分享你的快照！每張拍攝的照片都會生成可分享的圖片，非常適合展示你的攝影技巧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>注意：</strong>我們的翻譯由人工智慧引擎提供支持，可能不是 100% 準確。</p>", "short_description": "在 Sapphire Safari 中回應野性的召喚！這是一款開放世界的攝影冒險遊戲！捕捉現實中的怪物女孩在自然棲息地中的美麗身影，使用各種工具吸引她們擺出更具誘惑性的姿勢，如果你有足夠的勇氣……還可以與她們發展親密關係。", "supported_languages": "英文<strong>*</strong>, 法文, 義大利文, 德文, 西班牙文 - 西班牙, 日文, 波蘭文, 俄文, 簡體中文, 泰文, 繁體中文, 烏克蘭文, 韓文, 葡萄牙文 - 巴西, 土耳其文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/header.jpg?t=1775571253", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/714288ac166b88d10dac93c80e2db3c06eaf588c/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1775571253", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/714288ac166b88d10dac93c80e2db3c06eaf588c/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1775571253", "website": "http://www.kinkyfridays.com/", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10 64bits<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel i7-3370 or similar<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> GTX 970 or similar<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：11<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 5 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10 64bits<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel i5-9400F or similar<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 8 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> RTX 2060 or similar<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：12<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 5 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Ubuntu 16.04+<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel i7-3370 or similar<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> GTX 970 or similar<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 4 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Ubuntu 16.04+<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel i5-9400F or similar<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> RTX 2060 or similar<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 4 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "legal_notice": "Copyright © 2021. Kinky Fridays. Stay juicy. Stay kinky.", "developers": ["Kinky Fridays"], "publishers": ["Kinky Fridays"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 23800, "final": 23800, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "NT$ 238"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 28, "description": "完全支援控制器"}, {"id": 29, "description": "Steam 交換卡片"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "25", "description": "冒險"}, {"id": "4", "description": "休閒"}, {"id": "70", "description": "搶先體驗"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2025 年 3 月 21 日"}}}}, "us": {"1526900": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Sapphire Safari", "steam_appid": 1526900, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/f0fd0d53aa7146e29ecf25ab1d9b68e4.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sapphire Safari is still in early development, and many exciting features are coming shortly! Read our development posts for more details on upcoming content. The tasks below are not in any particular order; our goal is to get them all done!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/c54deaafb72f06205143310d35745d4e.avif?t=1775571253\" width=956 height=608 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/a0be4ce39685138a23db4534a666fd8e.avif?t=1775571253\" width=800 height=146 /></span></p></p><br><h1>SYSTEM SPECS</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sapphire Safari runs well on most systems, including more modern integrated graphics systems. Testing has been performed on Windows 11 with both Desktop and Laptop solutions. The most important hardware you can have is SSD storage and a good amount of VRAM.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/c3d86e14db17fb4b5146121fb380f478.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=472 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/2b117d55735fa861472b7bd4d3b63c48.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=476 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Answer the call of the wild with Sapphire Safari, an open-world Photography Adventure Game! Capture the beauty of real-life Monster Girls in their natural habitats. As a wildlife photographer, your job is to venture deep into unexplored territories, capture the Monster Girls as they socialize, hunt, sleep, mate, and hopefully come out in one piece.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/e32d8bd37796fafd14d194decbd6274d.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/1b37f5b34566df86b96177b9eb4433cf.poster.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/1b37f5b34566df86b96177b9eb4433cf.webm?t=1775571253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/1b37f5b34566df86b96177b9eb4433cf.mp4?t=1775571253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sapphire Island was mysteriously discovered, and a team of daring scientists were sent in to uncover its secrets. The lure of a virgin land to explore, teeming with unique wildlife, an amazing discovery! Who wouldn't be excited to chase this opportunity? A month passes, and the Science Team has lost contact with the home base. What will happen next?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/71a0f297cac82e7d683f1ed82f854dbd.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/c6b06392a3d29eaaf33e179de44de5e5.poster.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/c6b06392a3d29eaaf33e179de44de5e5.webm?t=1775571253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/c6b06392a3d29eaaf33e179de44de5e5.mp4?t=1775571253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the role of a wildlife photographer, seeking glory, and fame! Follow the tracks of the Science Team to discover their fate, while documenting the island in all its splendor! Fill out the Monster Encyclopedia with exotic photos, poses, mating acts, and intimate moments!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/ef3533818a09f3f7405def21306d8ce8.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=130 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/48cbb11059f92f48df10fe2c117bc015.poster.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/48cbb11059f92f48df10fe2c117bc015.webm?t=1775571253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/48cbb11059f92f48df10fe2c117bc015.mp4?t=1775571253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sapphire Island is teeming with unique wildlife, but not all are friendly. Stalk your way through the landscape and try to remain unnoticed, the island’s Predators love a tasty snack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/91c69249d224efb3f94424eff5ab042d.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=130 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/651652f7fd34c922955df0b5168c9b7d.poster.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/651652f7fd34c922955df0b5168c9b7d.webm?t=1775571253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/651652f7fd34c922955df0b5168c9b7d.mp4?t=1775571253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become one with the Natives! Spending time around the creatures will cause them to become friendly. Initiate intimate acts, engage in playful activities, and let the Wildlife pose for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/9059e1305aeb23d394f0d6be5ef75643.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete the Encyclopedia, Witness every Intimate Act, Recover lost Expedition Logs, Uncover the Island, Collect all Achievements, Unleash hidden dangers, and much more! Sapphire Safari offers a bounty of objectives to complete and mysteries to discover!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore environments, teeming with Monster Girls.<br>A full complement of voice acting by industry professionals.<br>Explore many unique locations and photograph/catalog the wildlife on display.<br>Bond with the Monster Girls in their unique environments, and experience new sensations!<br>Customize your experience with many sexual Flavors on offer! A veritable Anthro delight! <br>Complete your Encyclopedia and Discover all the Secrets! A rewarding collect-a-thon.<br>Day or Night. Rain, Storms, or Sunshine! Sapphire Island changes depending on the dynamic weather.<br>Share your Snaps! All photos taken produce shareable images, perfect for showing off your skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Answer the call of the wild and experience the incredibly unique adventure of Sapphire Safari!</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/2b117d55735fa861472b7bd4d3b63c48.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=476 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Answer the call of the wild with Sapphire Safari, an open-world Photography Adventure Game! Capture the beauty of real-life Monster Girls in their natural habitats. As a wildlife photographer, your job is to venture deep into unexplored territories, capture the Monster Girls as they socialize, hunt, sleep, mate, and hopefully come out in one piece.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/e32d8bd37796fafd14d194decbd6274d.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/1b37f5b34566df86b96177b9eb4433cf.poster.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/