=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become one with the Natives! Spending time around the creatures will cause them to become friendly. Initiate intimate acts, engage in playful activities, and let the Wildlife pose for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1526900/extras/9059e1305aeb23d394f0d6be5ef75643.avif?t=1775571253\" width=600 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete the Encyclopedia, Witness every Intimate Act, Recover lost Expedition Logs, Uncover the Island, Collect all Achievements, Unleash hidden dangers, and much more! Sapphire Safari offers a bounty of objectives to complete and mysteries to discover!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore environments, teeming with Monster Girls.<br>A full complement of voice acting by industry professionals.<br>Explore many unique locations and photograph/catalog the wildlife on display.<br>Bond with the Monster Girls in their unique environments, and experience new sensations!<br>Customize your experience with many sexual Flavors on offer! A veritable Anthro delight! <br>Complete your Encyclopedia and Discover all the Secrets! A rewarding collect-a-thon.<br>Day or Night. Rain, Storms, or Sunshine! Sapphire Island changes depending on the dynamic weather.<br>Share your Snaps! All photos taken produce shareable images, perfect for showing off your skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Answer the call of the wild and experience the incredibly unique adventure of Sapphire Safari!</p>", "short_description": "Answer the call of the wild with Sapphire Safari, an open-world Photography Adventure Game! Capture the beauty of real-life Monster Girls in their natural habitats, use tools to lure them into more erotic poses, and become intimate with them if you are brave enoug